doFilterInternal(HttpServletRequest, HttpServletResponse, FilterChain) - Method in class com.strangequark.userservice.config.JwtAuthenticationFilter
Perform the following operations in sequential order: -Check if the authorization header is null or does not start with "Bearer ", if true then go to the next filter and return -Set the value of jwtToken to the authorizationHeader, exlcuding the "Bearer " substring
